    "name": "Tour connect backend",
    "description": "This collection contains the core CRUD requests for the **Tours** resource in the Tour Connect backend API.\n\n### Base URL\n\nAll requests use the collection variable `{{BASE_URL}}` as the API host, e.g. `{{BASE_URL}}/tour`. Set `BASE_URL` to point to your running environment (local/dev/stage/prod).\n\n### Endpoints included (CRUD)\n\n- **Fetch all tours**: `GET {{BASE_URL}}/tour`\n    \n- **Get tour by ID**: `GET {{BASE_URL}}/tour/:id` (example request uses `102`)\n    \n- **Create a new tour**: `POST {{BASE_URL}}/tour`\n    \n- **Update tour details**: `PUT {{BASE_URL}}/tour/:id` (example request uses `102`)\n    \n- **Delete a tour**: `DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/tour/:id` (example request uses `102`)\n    \n\n### Notes\n\n- IDs like `102` are **sample values** used in request paths—replace them with a real tour ID from your environment.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "26328902"
  },
